  "dateModified": "2026-04-02",
  "datePublished": "2026-04-02",
  "description": "The structural demand that a nation's cast of folk types remain stable, so that anyone who deviates from the assigned genre figure becomes a narrative disruption requiring exclusion. The mechanism connecting genring to fascist violence: not the production of the genre figures themselves, but the pressure to keep them in their assigned positions.",
  "name": "Genre coherence",
